Interface System

  • All Superinterfaces:

    SystemImpl

    public interface System
extends OaamBaseElementA, VariantDependentElementA, ModeDependentElementA
    A representation of the model object 'System'. A system is an encapsuleted functionality that interacts with information and power

    The following features are supported:

    • Provided Outputs
    • Required Inputs
